text:
Bronx Park: A view of the Museum of the New York Botanical Garden. It is in the northwestern corner of the park, near Mosholu Parkway. This is a set of three views taken the same day.

May 12, 1938.

P. L. Sperr
title: Bronx: Bronx Park - Museum, N.Y. Botanical Garden.
